WEBVTT

00:01.317 --> 00:04.119
Cheers is filmed
before a live studio audience.

00:04.153 --> 00:05.820
Hey, Cliffie.
What you doing?

00:05.854 --> 00:09.074
Uh, writing a letter
of application for the Eco pod.

00:09.108 --> 00:10.542
What the heck's the Eco pod?

00:10.543 --> 00:12.744
It's a totally
self-contained environment

00:12.745 --> 00:15.881
located in a mile-wide bubble
underneath the desert floor.

00:15.915 --> 00:17.716
Yeah.

00:17.717 --> 00:20.134
It's gonna be inhabited
by the best and the brightest

00:20.135 --> 00:24.372
of the, uh, human species,
so I-I thought I'd apply.

00:24.374 --> 00:26.558
They're gonna have a zoo
in there, too?

00:26.592 --> 00:28.760
Yeah. Yeah, very
funny, Carla.

00:28.761 --> 00:30.679
You'll be laughing out of
the other side of your face

00:30.680 --> 00:33.181
when they make me Postmaster
General of the Eco pod.

00:33.182 --> 00:37.018
Actually, the Eco pod
does have some scientific merit.

00:37.019 --> 00:39.187
It was designed
by a colleague of Lilith's,

00:39.188 --> 00:40.455
Dr. Louis Pascal.

00:40.490 --> 00:41.940
It will serve as a prototype

00:41.941 --> 00:43.775
for the colonization of space.

00:43.776 --> 00:45.676
Plus which,
the grant money is incredible.

00:45.677 --> 00:47.612
I hear
Pascal's driving a Lexus.

00:49.282 --> 00:51.132
Boy, I sure hope I get a shot

00:51.167 --> 00:53.034
at being sealed
up in that thing.

00:53.036 --> 00:54.886
Say, would a petition help?

00:54.921 --> 00:57.188
It might.

00:57.189 --> 00:58.172
Hey, I'll sign that.

00:58.173 --> 00:59.307
No! I'm first!

00:59.341 --> 01:01.159
Okay...
Boy.

01:01.294 --> 01:04.178
(weepy): You guys are the best
friends a fellow ever had.

01:05.965 --> 01:07.732
(theme song begins)

01:09.635 --> 01:11.970
♪ Sometimes you want to go ♪

01:12.004 --> 01:16.441
♪ Where everybody
knows your name ♪

01:17.743 --> 01:22.380
♪ And they're always
glad you came ♪

01:22.414 --> 01:24.649
♪ You wanna be
where you can see ♪

01:24.684 --> 01:27.218
♪ Our troubles
are all the same ♪

01:27.252 --> 01:31.523
♪ You wanna go where
everybody knows your name. ♪

